      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept good-condition example that presents nicely overall and should make a solid driver. The body and paint show well from a normal distance, with the kind of minor age-related blemishes and wear you\u2019d expect on an older car rather than a fully restored or show-level finish. Trim and brightwork are presentable, and the interior is tidy and usable with visible signs of regular use but nothing that takes away from enjoying the car. Mechanically, it appears to be a sound, honest car you can get in and use, though buyers should expect normal maintenance needs consistent with age. A good, straightforward example for someone who wants a nice driver without paying mint-condition money.",
